    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality masterpiece that defies its age. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, and the condition is truly impeccable. The exterior finish is flawless, having been treated with a multi-stage paint correction and a professional-grade ceramic coating; the paint depth is incredible, with zero stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition. The premium leather upholstery is supple, showing no signs of bolster wear or creasing, and the interior retains its original factory scent. Every button, switch, and digital interface functions with crisp precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented, comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. It has recently undergone a full preventative maintenance cycle and sits on a fresh set of premium tires. This sale includes the original window sticker, two sets of keys, and all factory manuals. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
